\ul Configure Alert Settings\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ulnone\b0\fs24 For each organization and project, you can select which conditions trigger alerts and how users are notified.\par
\b Notification Options: \par
\b0 When you configure an alert, you select how notifications are sent. You can select multiple notification methods, such as email, text message, or team collaboration tools.\par
Atlas supports Slack as a notification method. From the organization's Settings menu, click Add to Slack in Slack Settings and log in to your preferred Slack workspace.\par
Atlas supports configuring all of the following notification methods during alert configuration:\par

